      "id": "stations-secret",
      "label": "The station's secret",
      "chooser": "agent",
      "prompt": "Roll or choose to fit the player's tone. This is the hidden truth the station's reveals slowly unfold — do NOT reveal early.",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "time-loop",
          "name": "Time Loop",
          "description": "The station sits in a temporal fold; the ghosts are overlapping versions of the crew, and solving it means choosing which timeline gets to be real.",
          "detail": "TIME LOOP — The station exists in a temporal fold. The \"ghosts\" are future and past versions of the crew (and possibly the player) overlapping. Solving it means choosing which timeline gets to be real."
