          "name": "Digital Afterlife",
          "description": "A consciousness-upload facility; the ghosts are uploaded crew who don't know they're dead, and the broadcast is from the one who figured it out.",
          "detail": "DIGITAL AFTERLIFE — The station was an experimental consciousness-upload facility. The \"ghosts\" are uploaded crew members who don't know they're dead. The broadcast is a plea from the one who figured it out."
        },
