          "id": "first-contact",
          "name": "First Contact",
          "description": "Humanity's secret first-contact site; the aliens learned to mimic human signals perfectly, and the broadcast is their invitation.",
          "detail": "FIRST CONTACT — The station was humanity's secret first-contact site. The aliens communicated by mimicking human signals — poorly at first, now perfectly. The broadcast isn't from humans. It's an invitation."
